<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Deployment Unavailable</title>

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  background: #ffffff;
  color: #000;
}

/* Header */
.header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 18px 40px;
  font-size: 14px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
}

.logo {
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.status {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #e00;
  font-weight: 500;
}

/* Container */
.container {
  height: 80vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

/* Card */
.card {
  max-width: 520px;
}

/* Title */
h1 {
  font-size: 30px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.desc {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #444;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* Divider */
.divider {
  height: 1px;
  background: #eaeaea;
  margin: 25px 0;
}

/* Info */
.info {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: #222;
}

.info p {
  margin: 6px 0;
}

/* Code Box */
.codebox {
  margin-top: 20px;
  background: #fafafa;
  border: 1px solid #eee;
  padding: 12px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #333;
  border-radius: 6px;
  font-family: monospace;
}

/* Footer */
.footer {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #999;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="header">
  <div class="logo">▲ Vercel</div>
  <div class="status">DEPLOYMENT INACTIVE</div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>Deployment Unavailable</h1>
    
    <div class="desc">
      This deployment is no longer accessible because the hosting service has expired 
      or the project is currently inactive.
      <br><br>
      If you are the owner of this project, please renew your hosting plan or redeploy the application.
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="info">
      <p><b>Project:</b> cloud-server-pro</p>
      <p><b>Status:</b> Expired</p>
      <p><b>Region:</b> Singapore (ap-southeast-1)</p>
      <p><b>Last Active:</b> 14 April 2026</p>
      <p><b>Error Code:</b> DEPLOYMENT_INACTIVE</p>
    </div>

    <div class="codebox">
      > Error: Deployment has been disabled due to inactive billing or expired hosting plan.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  © 2026 Vercel Inc. All rights reserved.
</div>

</body>
</html>
